WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.230 --> 00:00:04.560
The moment you step on board

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:09.170
Pont-Aven your holiday really has begun.

00:00:09.170 --> 00:00:12.960
The ship boasts a stunning array of
features you'd expect

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:19.320
on a cruise liner.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:23.289
Pont-Aven is Brittany Ferries flagship
taking her name from the Breton

00:00:23.289 --> 00:00:26.970
town synonymous with artists and her
interior decor

00:00:26.970 --> 00:00:29.250
reflects that link.

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:34.150
Leaving port the perfect place to enjoy
the view is the spectacular wrap-around

00:00:34.150 --> 00:00:35.760
promenade deck.

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:37.930
 

00:00:37.930 --> 00:00:44.930
 

00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:01.980
For a spot of retail therapy, our shopping malls sells an excellent range of wines,

00:01:01.980 --> 00:01:07.509
spirits, tobacco, perfume, gifts and travel
essentials.

00:01:07.509 --> 00:01:11.549
Children are well catered for, with a
playroom as well as a special program

00:01:11.549 --> 00:01:12.460
of entertainment.

00:01:12.460 --> 00:01:17.170
Meanwhile, teenagers can head for the
Games Planet.

00:01:17.170 --> 00:01:23.790
 

00:01:23.790 --> 00:01:26.990
 

00:01:26.990 --> 00:01:31.030
There's a stylish range of accommodation on Pont-Aven. Top-of-the-range

00:01:31.030 --> 00:01:35.210
are the outside 4 berth Commodore Cabins.

00:01:35.210 --> 00:01:41.710
Standard cabins range from outside 4
berth to inside 2 berth.

00:01:41.710 --> 00:01:45.040
And if you want to travel with the
family dog, kennels are available

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:47.710
on longer sailings.

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:51.230
The central hub of the ship is the main
lounge bar,  Le Grand Pavois.

00:01:51.230 --> 00:01:55.690
It's also a focal point for some
spectacular live entertainment.

00:01:55.690 --> 00:01:57.670
 

00:01:57.670 --> 00:02:04.670
Our stylish cocktail bar Le Fastnet, is
the perfect place for an aperitif.

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:08.830
No voyage with Brittany Ferries is complete without sampling some great French

00:02:08.830 --> 00:02:09.490
cuisine.

00:02:09.490 --> 00:02:14.160
Le Flora restaurant offers superb
dining with a choice a fine wines.

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:19.230
For a more casual experience La Belle Angèle is Pont-Aven's self-service

00:02:19.230 --> 00:02:19.920
restaurant.

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:26.920
And for drinks and light bites try
Le Café du Festival.

00:02:27.670 --> 00:02:32.130
Try our award-winning service on Pont-Aven next time you travel to France or

00:02:32.130 --> 00:02:33.590
Spain.

00:02:33.590 --> 00:02:35.819
 

